== Welcome to Hitchhiker

Hitchhiker is my academic (University of Wroc≈Çaw) Ruby on Rails course project, developed for purpose of teaching rails and web applications technologies.

Hitchhiker is a portal dedicated to people looking for or offering transport. Users can make account to use full functionality of service or just browsing offers as a guest.


-- Used technologies

  - Rails v. 3.1.0
  - postgresql v. 1.12.2
  - CoffeScript
  - Haml
  - Sass
  - Google Maps Api

-- Try out

  http://hitchhiker.herokuapp.com/
  
